<div id="wrapper"><h2><a href="/output/Page2.asp"><img alt="" height="70" src="../files/images/XM_logo.gif" title="XM London Digital Communication" width="162" /></a></h2><h2><img width="261" alt="Technical and hosting" height="80" border="0" src="/files/images/XM_L3_What_technical_shdr.gif" /></h2><p>We have an in house technical and programming department to ensure that all the creative solutions and recommendations we make maximize the possibilities of the environment and technology. From integration to the development of tailor made applications, the technical department work as integral parts of our teams. </p><p>When it comes to designing and developing within content management solutions we have worked with the leading players, including BroadVision, Vignette, OpenMarket and have a great understanding of the issues and challenges involved in successfully deploying a CMS. </p><p>We have also developed our own CMS, Net Dev Plus, which has been successfully deployed on many of websites for major corporations and government departments both in the UK and overseas. For more information please visit <a href="http://www.netdevplus.net/" target="_blank">www.netdevplus.net</a> or contact <a href="mailto:awalters@xmlondon.com">Ainsley Walters</a> to arrange a demonstration.</p><p>We host and manage websites for a number of our clients. Sites can be hosted either in our own secure server room, or on your premises. Security staff are on duty 24 hours a day, 365 days a year at our premises, and our server room is alarmed whenever unoccupied, and protected round the clock by closed-circuit television and infrared cameras. Keys to the server room are signed out by security staff to a controlled list of authorised personnel. </p><img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" />
